Command> gh issue edit [issue number] --title [hoge] --body [geho]   # イシュー番号の編集


Keywords> github

Description>
           > --add-assignee     <login>
           > --add-label        <name>
           > --add-project      <name>
           > -b, --body         <string>
           > -F, --body-file    <file>
           > --remove-assignee  <login>
           > --remove-label     <name>
           > --remove-project   <name>
           > -t, --title        <string>
           >
           >
           >
           >
           >
           >

SCENE01> gh issue edit 23 --title "I found a bug" --body "Nothing works"
SCENE02> gh issue edit 23 --add-label "bug,help wanted" --remove-label "core"
SCENE03> gh issue edit 23 --add-assignee "@me" --remove-assignee monalisa,hubot
SCENE04> gh issue edit 23 --add-project "Roadmap" --remove-project v1,v2
SCENE05> gh issue edit 23 --milestone "Version 1"
SCENE06> gh issue edit 23 --body-file body.txt
SCENE07> gh issue edit 23 34 --add-label "help wanted"



Reference> https://dev.classmethod.jp/articles/i-tried-operations-around-issue-with-github-cli-20/


